commit_message: Updated with latest cnv script, also updated reference and annotation with BILS. Removed a lot of uneeded code
Fixed minor bugs and added segment_CNV to the CNV output
Commented out BAQ - redundant. Renamed previous bam output to not mess up downstream use
Added VarScan as SNP caller, commented out Freebayes related rows
One dash too much at line 132
Added -F to freebayes snp calling to lower the allele frequency threshold
BUGFIX: Wrong bam-file for VARW calculation
BUGFIX: Wrong bam file (non-existing) as input for indel calling by varscan
Removed GATK local realignment, redundant with BAQ
SETTINGS: Changed reference bam file for CNV calling
Known Issues: Added information about realignment
Removed dysfunctional overlap of sliding window from cnv_pipe.pl parameters
Added feature: Added a cutoff of region length to keep in the output file. Usage: cnv_merger file [cutoff] > outputfile. Default is set to 1000
Missed moving one file to the folder intermediate files
Added more files to be removed to intermediate files folder
BUGFIX: Fixed error due to removal of output column in cnv_pipe.pl. Adjusted the column numbers
Fixed syntax error in filter expression of the VARW filter
Added feature: Move all intermediate file into a separate folder inte the main output folder
Fixed FORMAT line in vcf output header
